        "title": "Second Disaster",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Second Disaster comes approximately at the middle of Act 2, roughly 50% of the way into your story. Your lead Character has spent the first half of Act 2 trying to achieve their story goal, but they've been pursuing a path that won't work. The Second Disaster is a bad thing that happens at the midpoint of the story that forces your Protagonist to try a new approach. This new approach will actually work. "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Example – Star Wars:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "In the original Star Wars movie (Episode 4), Obi-Wan Kenobi is killed by Darth Vader at the midpoint of the story. Up till now, Luke has been following Obi-Wan and just doing what he says. Now he has to step up and start making his own decisions--and he needs to actually start using the Force. He will never win unless he becomes strong in the Force, and he has the second half of Act 2 to get strong."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% to 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Second Disaster occurs around the 50% mark of the story."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
